    "en": {
      "title": "Action in London\u2026",
      "author": "Sahan Weerasooriya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Rajiv Sebastian and his band The Clan have always been very active in the scene here\u2026and abroad.",
        "They were seen in action in Dubai and Oman early this year and will now be travelling to London, next month, to entertain guests at a dinner dance.",
        "\u2018Rhythms of Sri Lanka\u2019 will be held, on August 13th, at the Thistle Hotel Heathrow.",
        "Rajiv also worked on a very special song to celebrate the 78th birthday of the late Desmond de Silva, which fell on July 13th.",
        "With the assistance of several other known artistes, he came up with \u2018Desmondge Wathagotha.\u2019",
        "Leave a Reply Cancel replyYour email address will not be published. Required fields are marked *Comment Name *",
        "Save my name, email, and website in this browser for the next time I comment."
      ],
